MADISON
The Butcher
HT: 5'2
WT: 109lbs

A great battle between two evenly ranked opponents. 8th vs 11th - who fucking who?
Madison is a seasoned veteran. Tough, tenacious, quick and strong. She understands the sport and loves fucking the losers.
Ami is a favorite to win the first annual rookie of the year award this season. She lost her first two matches, but those defeats are what made her what she is today. Her size and strength demand that every wrestler take her seriously. She is that good.
title: Ami "The Valkyrie" Emerson (1-2)
